articles.title: Elvis Presley to become AI hologram in London - The A.V. Club
articles.description: Elvis Presley will be resurrected through the power of artificial intelligence in the new U.K. show Elvis Evolution
articles.content: Lots of big stars have played Elvis in recent years: first Oscar nominee Austin Butler, then Internet heartthrob Jacob Elordi, and now the name on everyones lips, artificial intelligence. Yes, be you… [+2909 chars]
